Dialogue: 100,0:01:24.72,0:01:25.20,Normal Dialog Text,General,0,0,0,,{\fn微软雅黑\fs64}哈！\N{\fnArial\fs48}Ha!
Dialogue: 100,0:01:25.44,0:01:28.60,Normal Dialog Text,General,0,0,0,,{\fn微软雅黑\fs64}对不起，但你走错方-向-了！\N{\fnArial\fs48}Sorry. But you're going the wrong way!
Dialogue: 100,0:01:30.32,0:01:31.02,Normal Dialog Text,General,0,0,0,,{\fn微软雅黑\fs64}抓住她！\N{\fnArial\fs48}Get her!
Dialogue: 100,0:01:39.60,0:01:40.70,Normal Dialog Text,General,0,0,0,,{\fn微软雅黑\fs64}你没打中哦\N{\fnArial\fs48}You missed.
