Dialogue: 100,0:01:41.50,0:01:41.90,Normal Dialog Text,General,0,0,0,,{\fn微软雅黑\fs64}呃？\N{\fnArial\fs48}Huh?
Dialogue: 100,0:01:44.88,0:01:48.16,Normal Dialog Text,General,0,0,0,,{\fn微软雅黑\fs64}啊～这个破烂星球就没一个正常工作的东西吗？\N{\fnArial\fs48}Ah, doesn't anything work on this cruddy planet?
