Dialogue: 100,0:02:05.92,0:02:08.22,Normal Dialog Text,General,0,0,0,,{\fn微软雅黑\fs64}对不起，对不～对不～对不～对不~对不起\N{\fnArial\fs48}I'm sorry. I'm sorry. I'm sorry. I'm sorry. I'm sorry. I'm sorry.
