Dialogue: 100,0:02:15.16,0:02:17.06,Normal Dialog Text,General,0,0,0,,{\fn微软雅黑\fs64}\N{\fnArial\fs48}Nyeh!
Dialogue: 100,0:02:19.02,0:02:20.30,Normal Dialog Text,General,0,0,0,,{\fn微软雅黑\fs64}周末愉快！\N{\fnArial\fs48}Have a great weekend.
Dialogue: 100,0:02:21.88,0:02:25.04,Normal Dialog Text,General,0,0,0,,{\fn微软雅黑\fs64}我是指，我，希望，她的周末，不怎么，愉快？\N{\fnArial\fs48}I mean, I hope her weekend is not so great.
Dialogue: 100,0:02:28.12,0:02:31.06,Normal Dialog Text,General,0,0,0,,{\fn微软雅黑\fs64}好吧，我有意识到了刚才算是惨败\N{\fnArial\fs48}Okay, I realize that was a bit of a fiasco.
Dialogue: 100,0:02:31.24,0:02:33.06,Normal Dialog Text,General,0,0,0,,{\fn微软雅黑\fs64}但还是有点收获的！\N{\fnArial\fs48}But there's a silver lining to this.
