Dialogue: 100,0:02:36.66,0:02:38.16,Normal Dialog Text,General,0,0,0,,{\fn微软雅黑\fs64}每当她使用传送系统时\N{\fnArial\fs48}Whenever she uses the warp system,
Dialogue: 100,0:02:38.16,0:02:41.26,Normal Dialog Text,General,0,0,0,,{\fn微软雅黑\fs64}她的逃生舱会立刻探测到她在哪里\N{\fnArial\fs48}her escape pod will instantly detect exactly where she is.
Dialogue: 100,0:02:41.40,0:02:43.46,Normal Dialog Text,General,0,0,0,,{\fn微软雅黑\fs64}我们抓到她只是个时间问题，\N{\fnArial\fs48}It's only a matter of time until we catch her,
Dialogue: 100,0:02:43.46,0:02:46.18,Normal Dialog Text,General,0,0,0,,{\fn微软雅黑\fs64}而且当我们做到时，我们就能放下之前的问题，\N{\fnArial\fs48}and when we do, we'll be able to close this chapter
Dialogue: 100,0:02:46.18,0:02:48.26,Normal Dialog Text,General,0,0,0,,{\fn微软雅黑\fs64}并最终再次前进，对吧？\N{\fnArial\fs48}and finally move on, right?
Dialogue: 100,0:02:55.92,0:02:58.36,Normal Dialog Text,General,0,0,0,,{\fn微软雅黑\fs64}有没有什么可能是你们两个\N{\fnArial\fs48}Isn't there something that maybe the two of you
Dialogue: 100,0:02:58.36,0:03:00.62,Normal Dialog Text,General,0,0,0,,{\fn微软雅黑\fs64}也许要谈谈的？\N{\fnArial\fs48}might need to talk about?
Dialogue: 100,0:03:03.60,0:03:04.38,Normal Dialog Text,General,0,0,0,,{\fn微软雅黑\fs64}是橄榄石\N{\fnArial\fs48}It's Peridot.
Dialogue: 100,0:03:04.66,0:03:06.36,Normal Dialog Text,General,0,0,0,,{\fn微软雅黑\fs64}她现在就在使用传送台\N{\fnArial\fs48}She's using the warps right now.
Dialogue: 100,0:03:07.32,0:03:09.04,Normal Dialog Text,General,0,0,0,,{\fn微软雅黑\fs64}看，她就在这里\N{\fnArial\fs48}Look. This is where she is.
Dialogue: 100,0:03:09.60,0:03:11.20,Normal Dialog Text,General,0,0,0,,{\fn微软雅黑\fs64}这次我们肯定能抓住她了\N{\fnArial\fs48}We got her for sure this time.
Dialogue: 100,0:03:11.68,0:03:13.50,Normal Dialog Text,General,0,0,0,,{\fn微软雅黑\fs64}如果她认为她是占上风的话，\N{\fnArial\fs48}If she thinks she's got the upper hand,
