Dialogue: 100,0:03:19.98,0:03:22.30,Normal Dialog Text,General,0,0,0,,{\fn微软雅黑\fs64}呃，至少珍珠还很乐观\N{\fnArial\fs48}Well, at least Pearl's optimistic.
