Dialogue: 100,0:03:26.98,0:03:28.88,Normal Dialog Text,General,0,0,0,,{\fn微软雅黑\fs64}但这并不能弥补她为了和\N{\fnArial\fs48}but it won't make up for the stunt she pulled
Dialogue: 100,0:03:28.88,0:03:30.74,Normal Dialog Text,General,0,0,0,,{\fn微软雅黑\fs64}石榴融合而编织的骗局\N{\fnArial\fs48}to get Garnet to fuse with her.
Dialogue: 100,0:03:31.74,0:03:33.07,Normal Dialog Text,General,0,0,0,,{\fn微软雅黑\fs64}史蒂文，咱们走！\N{\fnArial\fs48}Steven, let's go.
Dialogue: 100,0:03:35.88,0:03:36.81,Normal Dialog Text,General,0,0,0,,{\fn微软雅黑\fs64}喔\N{\fnArial\fs48}Whoa.
Dialogue: 100,0:03:37.22,0:03:38.90,Normal Dialog Text,General,0,0,0,,{\fn微软雅黑\fs64}哈！她太过绝望了\N{\fnArial\fs48}Ha! She's desperate.
Dialogue: 100,0:03:39.12,0:03:41.54,Normal Dialog Text,General,0,0,0,,{\fn微软雅黑\fs64}看看！她把自己困在了那里\N{\fnArial\fs48}Look at this. She's cornered herself in there.
Dialogue: 100,0:03:41.74,0:03:42.26,Normal Dialog Text,General,0,0,0,,{\fn微软雅黑\fs64}\N{\fnArial\fs48}Hmm.
Dialogue: 100,0:03:42.58,0:03:44.72,Normal Dialog Text,General,0,0,0,,{\fn微软雅黑\fs64}我们刚好让她到了我们想要的地方\N{\fnArial\fs48}We've got her just where we want her.
Dialogue: 100,0:03:45.34,0:03:45.82,Normal Dialog Text,General,0,0,0,,{\fn微软雅黑\fs64}这是-\N{\fnArial\fs48}What is --
Dialogue: 100,0:03:45.82,0:03:47.34,Normal Dialog Text,General,0,0,0,,{\fn微软雅黑\fs64}好问题，史蒂文\N{\fnArial\fs48}excellent question, Steven.
Dialogue: 100,0:03:47.54,0:03:48.66,Normal Dialog Text,General,0,0,0,,{\fn微软雅黑\fs64}我们现在看到的\N{\fnArial\fs48}What we see before us
Dialogue: 100,0:03:48.66,0:03:50.92,Normal Dialog Text,General,0,0,0,,{\fn微软雅黑\fs64}是个原始的星际宝石飞船\N{\fnArial\fs48}is an ancient interplanetary gem vessel.
Dialogue: 100,0:03:51.18,0:03:54.22,Normal Dialog Text,General,0,0,0,,{\fn微软雅黑\fs64}母世界的宝石人们通过这些飞船穿越太空\N{\fnArial\fs48}Homeworld gems used these ships to travel across the cosmos
Dialogue: 100,0:03:54.22,0:03:56.62,Normal Dialog Text,General,0,0,0,,{\fn微软雅黑\fs64}来到地球-这当然是在传送台建成之前\N{\fnArial\fs48}and land here on earth before the warp pads were built.
Dialogue: 100,0:03:56.92,0:03:59.00,Normal Dialog Text,General,0,0,0,,{\fn微软雅黑\fs64}但这些飞船在这里待了太长时间了\N{\fnArial\fs48}But these ships landed here so long ago
Dialogue: 100,0:03:59.00,0:04:00.80,Normal Dialog Text,General,0,0,0,,{\fn微软雅黑\fs64}不可能还可以正常工作\N{\fnArial\fs48}that there's no way they can be functional.
Dialogue: 100,0:04:01.08,0:04:02.68,Normal Dialog Text,General,0,0,0,,{\fn微软雅黑\fs64}橄榄石没什么选择余地了\N{\fnArial\fs48}Peridot's running out of options.
Dialogue: 100,0:04:02.78,0:04:04.84,Normal Dialog Text,General,0,0,0,,{\fn微软雅黑\fs64}珍珠，我们可不能浪费时间\N{\fnArial\fs48}Pearl, we can't waste time.
Dialogue: 100,0:04:05.08,0:04:06.04,Normal Dialog Text,General,0,0,0,,{\fn微软雅黑\fs64}让我们专注于任务-\N{\fnArial\fs48}Let's focus on the task at --
Dialogue: 100,0:04:06.04,0:04:08.12,Normal Dialog Text,General,0,0,0,,{\fn微软雅黑\fs64}啊，对，手头的任务\N{\fnArial\fs48}ah, yes. The task at hand.
Dialogue: 100,0:04:08.28,0:04:10.44,Normal Dialog Text,General,0,0,0,,{\fn微软雅黑\fs64}不能瞎聊了，让我们一起抓橄榄石吧！\N{\fnArial\fs48}No more doddling. Let's go get Peridot!
Dialogue: 100,0:04:16.08,0:04:18.88,Normal Dialog Text,General,0,0,0,,{\fn微软雅黑\fs64}这看起来更像是个温室，而非太空飞船\N{\fnArial\fs48}It's more like a greenhouse than a spaceship.
Dialogue: 100,0:04:19.22,0:04:20.96,Normal Dialog Text,General,0,0,0,,{\fn微软雅黑\fs64}看来地球赢得了这场斗争\N{\fnArial\fs48}Looks like earth won this battle.
Dialogue: 100,0:04:22.26,0:04:22.82,Normal Dialog Text,General,0,0,0,,{\fn微软雅黑\fs64}哦\N{\fnArial\fs48}Oh.
Dialogue: 100,0:04:27.08,0:04:29.74,Normal Dialog Text,General,0,0,0,,{\fn微软雅黑\fs64}你们这些宝石人真是比渣土还蠢\N{\fnArial\fs48}You gems really are as dull as dirt.
Dialogue: 100,0:04:29.90,0:04:32.88,Normal Dialog Text,General,0,0,0,,{\fn微软雅黑\fs64}你才是蠢货，如果你觉得你能飞的了这破烂的话\N{\fnArial\fs48}You're the dull one if you think you can fly this wreck.
Dialogue: 100,0:04:33.72,0:04:35.94,Normal Dialog Text,General,0,0,0,,{\fn微软雅黑\fs64}啊？你说话能大声点吗？\N{\fnArial\fs48}What? Can you speak louder?
Dialogue: 100,0:04:36.26,0:04:37.82,Normal Dialog Text,General,0,0,0,,{\fn微软雅黑\fs64}有的通讯器报销了\N{\fnArial\fs48}Some of these communicators are gunked up.
Dialogue: 100,0:04:39.84,0:04:42.02,Normal Dialog Text,General,0,0,0,,{\fn微软雅黑\fs64}珍珠说，你才是蠢货\N{\fnArial\fs48}Pearl says you're the dull one
Dialogue: 100,0:04:42.02,0:04:43.76,Normal Dialog Text,General,0,0,0,,{\fn微软雅黑\fs64}如果你认为你能飞的了这破烂\N{\fnArial\fs48}if you think you can fly this wreck.
Dialogue: 100,0:04:47.82,0:04:48.70,Normal Dialog Text,General,0,0,0,,{\fn微软雅黑\fs64}飞？\N{\fnArial\fs48}Fly?
Dialogue: 100,0:04:48.86,0:04:51.36,Normal Dialog Text,General,0,0,0,,{\fn微软雅黑\fs64}我可不是要飞这艘飞船\N{\fnArial\fs48}I'm not using this vessel to fly.
Dialogue: 100,0:04:51.68,0:04:53.54,Normal Dialog Text,General,0,0,0,,{\fn微软雅黑\fs64}我是用它来困住你们的！\N{\fnArial\fs48}I'm using it to trap you!
Dialogue: 100,0:04:54.74,0:04:56.10,Normal Dialog Text,General,0,0,0,,{\fn微软雅黑\fs64}这很好吧？\N{\fnArial\fs48}Isn't this nice?
Dialogue: 100,0:04:56.34,0:04:58.76,Normal Dialog Text,General,0,0,0,,{\fn微软雅黑\fs64}不再有水晶战士四处乱跑\N{\fnArial\fs48}No more crystal gems running around,
Dialogue: 100,0:04:58.76,0:05:01.12,Normal Dialog Text,General,0,0,0,,{\fn微软雅黑\fs64}打乱我的计划，破坏我的物品\N{\fnArial\fs48}messing with my plans, destroying my things.
Dialogue: 100,0:05:01.48,0:05:03.88,Normal Dialog Text,General,0,0,0,,{\fn微软雅黑\fs64}看来我刚好让你们出现在我想要的位置\N{\fnArial\fs48}Looks like I've got you just where I want you.
Dialogue: 100,0:05:04.08,0:05:07.46,Normal Dialog Text,General,0,0,0,,{\fn微软雅黑\fs64}感觉怎么样，如此轻易的被算计，你们这群草包？！\N{\fnArial\fs48}How does it feel to be so easily outsmarted, you clods?!
Dialogue: 100,0:05:07.96,0:05:08.38,Normal Dialog Text,General,0,0,0,,{\fn微软雅黑\fs64}不\N{\fnArial\fs48}No.
Dialogue: 100,0:05:08.78,0:05:10.56,Normal Dialog Text,General,0,0,0,,{\fn微软雅黑\fs64}嘿，呃...我是紫晶\N{\fnArial\fs48}Hey, uh... This is Amethyst.
Dialogue: 100,0:05:10.72,0:05:13.08,Normal Dialog Text,General,0,0,0,,{\fn微软雅黑\fs64}我可不喜欢被叫做草包，你个草-\N{\fnArial\fs48}I don't appreciate being called a clod, you clo--
Dialogue: 100,0:05:13.08,0:05:13.86,Normal Dialog Text,General,0,0,0,,{\fn微软雅黑\fs64}说够了\N{\fnArial\fs48}enough talk.
Dialogue: 100,0:05:14.18,0:05:16.86,Normal Dialog Text,General,0,0,0,,{\fn微软雅黑\fs64}准备好迎接毁灭吧！\N{\fnArial\fs48}Prepare yourselves for annihilation!
Dialogue: 100,0:05:17.08,0:05:17.46,Normal Dialog Text,General,0,0,0,,{\fn微软雅黑\fs64}\N{\fnArial\fs48}Hyah!
Dialogue: 100,0:05:21.68,0:05:22.18,Normal Dialog Text,General,0,0,0,,{\fn微软雅黑\fs64}\N{\fnArial\fs48}Hyah.
Dialogue: 100,0:05:23.70,0:05:25.14,Normal Dialog Text,General,0,0,0,,{\fn微软雅黑\fs64}啊！这个还能用\N{\fnArial\fs48}Aha! It works.
Dialogue: 100,0:05:25.60,0:05:26.24,Normal Dialog Text,General,0,0,0,,{\fn微软雅黑\fs64}好！\N{\fnArial\fs48}Yes!
Dialogue: 100,0:05:26.82,0:05:30.34,Normal Dialog Text,General,0,0,0,,{\fn微软雅黑\fs64}去死死死死死死死死死死死死吧！\N{\fnArial\fs48}Die! Die! Die! Die! Die! Die! Die! Die! Die! Die! Die! Die! Die~!
Dialogue: 600,0:05:30.00,0:05:31.00,Hint,,0,0,0,,{\pos(960,50)}像不像美国队长？
Dialogue: 100,0:05:30.70,0:05:32.16,Normal Dialog Text,General,0,0,0,,{\fn微软雅黑\fs64}嘿，伙计们，这里\N{\fnArial\fs48}Hey, guys, over here.
Dialogue: 100,0:05:34.30,0:05:34.86,Normal Dialog Text,General,0,0,0,,{\fn微软雅黑\fs64}这个方向\N{\fnArial\fs48}This way.
Dialogue: 100,0:05:40.28,0:05:41.98,Normal Dialog Text,General,0,0,0,,{\fn微软雅黑\fs64}你真是太屌了，史蒂文！\N{\fnArial\fs48}You're on fire, Steven!
Dialogue: 100,0:05:42.64,0:05:44.68,Normal Dialog Text,General,0,0,0,,{\fn微软雅黑\fs64}那可是一天内三个盾啊\N{\fnArial\fs48}That's three shields in one day.
Dialogue: 100,0:05:45.00,0:05:46.26,Normal Dialog Text,General,0,0,0,,{\fn微软雅黑\fs64}可不算差了！\N{\fnArial\fs48}Not too shabby!
Dialogue: 100,0:05:47.66,0:05:48.16,Normal Dialog Text,General,0,0,0,,{\fn微软雅黑\fs64}快走！\N{\fnArial\fs48}Move!
Dialogue: 100,0:05:49.96,0:05:53.04,Normal Dialog Text,General,0,0,0,,{\fn微软雅黑\fs64}尖刺！你们喜欢我的尖刺吗？！\N{\fnArial\fs48}Spikes! How do you like my spikes?!
Dialogue: 100,0:05:53.48,0:05:54.46,Normal Dialog Text,General,0,0,0,,{\fn微软雅黑\fs64}橄榄石！\N{\fnArial\fs48}Peridot!
Dialogue: 100,0:05:54.60,0:05:55.64,Normal Dialog Text,General,0,0,0,,{\fn微软雅黑\fs64}珍珠，不要-\N{\fnArial\fs48}Pearl, don't just --
Dialogue: 100,0:05:58.92,0:06:00.20,Normal Dialog Text,General,0,0,0,,{\fn微软雅黑\fs64}你个笨蛋\N{\fnArial\fs48}You idiot.
Dialogue: 100,0:06:02.34,0:06:04.52,Normal Dialog Text,General,0,0,0,,{\fn微软雅黑\fs64}啊！呀！呀！呀！\N{\fnArial\fs48}Aah! Aah! Aah! Aah! Aah!
Dialogue: 100,0:06:08.28,0:06:10.58,Normal Dialog Text,General,0,0,0,,{\fn微软雅黑\fs64}珍珠，停下，这没有用\N{\fnArial\fs48}Pearl, stop. That isn't helping.
Dialogue: 100,0:06:10.84,0:06:12.34,Normal Dialog Text,General,0,0,0,,{\fn微软雅黑\fs64}我总得做点什么吧？\N{\fnArial\fs48}I have to do something.
Dialogue: 100,0:06:12.82,0:06:15.74,Normal Dialog Text,General,0,0,0,,{\fn微软雅黑\fs64}我不敢相信我直接将我们带进了橄榄石的陷阱\N{\fnArial\fs48}I can't believe I walked us right into Peridot's trap.
Dialogue: 100,0:06:16.48,0:06:18.96,Normal Dialog Text,General,0,0,0,,{\fn微软雅黑\fs64}这都是我的...错误？\N{\fnArial\fs48}This is all my...Fault?
Dialogue: 100,0:06:19.40,0:06:20.08,Normal Dialog Text,General,0,0,0,,{\fn微软雅黑\fs64}\N{\fnArial\fs48}Huh?
Dialogue: 100,0:06:22.00,0:06:25.08,Normal Dialog Text,General,0,0,0,,{\fn微软雅黑\fs64}啊～～～～～～！\N{\fnArial\fs48}Aah!
Dialogue: 100,0:06:25.08,0:06:25.88,Normal Dialog Text,General,0,0,0,,{\fn微软雅黑\fs64}呃？\N{\fnArial\fs48}Huh?
Dialogue: 100,0:06:28.18,0:06:29.36,Normal Dialog Text,General,0,0,0,,{\fn微软雅黑\fs64}我抓住你了，史蒂文\N{\fnArial\fs48}I got you, Steven.
Dialogue: 100,0:06:29.90,0:06:31.02,Normal Dialog Text,General,0,0,0,,{\fn微软雅黑\fs64}谢谢，紫晶\N{\fnArial\fs48}Thanks, Amethyst.
Dialogue: 100,0:06:32.26,0:06:33.20,Normal Dialog Text,General,0,0,0,,{\fn微软雅黑\fs64}石榴和珍珠\N{\fnArial\fs48}Garnet and Pearl.
Dialogue: 100,0:06:33.52,0:06:34.62,Normal Dialog Text,General,0,0,0,,{\fn微软雅黑\fs64}你们还好吗？\N{\fnArial\fs48}Are you guys okay?
Dialogue: 100,0:06:34.84,0:06:35.90,Normal Dialog Text,General,0,0,0,,{\fn微软雅黑\fs64}我们很好\N{\fnArial\fs48}We're fine.
Dialogue: 100,0:06:36.96,0:06:37.70,Normal Dialog Text,General,0,0,0,,{\fn微软雅黑\fs64}遭了\N{\fnArial\fs48}Crud.
Dialogue: 100,0:06:45.22,0:06:46.48,Normal Dialog Text,General,0,0,0,,{\fn微软雅黑\fs64}我们得救她们出来！\N{\fnArial\fs48}We've got to get them out.
Dialogue: 100,0:06:49.18,0:06:50.48,Normal Dialog Text,General,0,0,0,,{\fn微软雅黑\fs64}紫晶，我们该怎么-\N{\fnArial\fs48}Amethyst, what should we --
Dialogue: 100,0:06:50.48,0:06:52.44,Normal Dialog Text,General,0,0,0,,{\fn微软雅黑\fs64}石榴，我对不起\N{\fnArial\fs48}Pearl: Garnet, I'm sorry.
Dialogue: 100,0:06:52.44,0:06:53.02,Normal Dialog Text,General,0,0,0,,{\fn微软雅黑\fs64}等下\N{\fnArial\fs48}Wait a sec.
Dialogue: 100,0:06:53.24,0:06:55.74,Normal Dialog Text,Pearl,0,0,0,,{\fn微软雅黑\fs64\c&HDDF699&}事情本不应变成这样的\N{\fnArial\fs48}Things weren't supposed to turn out this way.
Dialogue: 100,0:06:57.12,0:06:58.56,Normal Dialog Text,Garnet,0,0,0,,{\fn微软雅黑\fs64\c&H811CC0&}我们总能离开的\N{\fnArial\fs48}We'll get out of here somehow.
Dialogue: 100,0:06:58.86,0:07:00.58,Normal Dialog Text,Pearl,0,0,0,,{\fn微软雅黑\fs64\c&HDDF699&}我不是这个意思\N{\fnArial\fs48}That's not what I mean.
Dialogue: 100,0:07:01.10,0:07:04.90,Normal Dialog Text,Pearl,0,0,0,,{\fn微软雅黑\fs64\c&HDDF699&}我非常想抓住橄榄石，以弥补我犯下的错误\N{\fnArial\fs48}I really wanted to catch Peridot to make up for what I did.
Dialogue: 100,0:07:05.80,0:07:07.32,Normal Dialog Text,Pearl,0,0,0,,{\fn微软雅黑\fs64\c&HDDF699&}我想向你证明-\N{\fnArial\fs48}I wanted to prove to you that --
Dialogue: 100,0:07:07.76,0:07:09.54,Normal Dialog Text,Pearl,0,0,0,,{\fn微软雅黑\fs64\c&HDDF699&}一切都能变回正常的样子\N{\fnArial\fs48}that everything could go back to normal.
Dialogue: 100,0:07:09.76,0:07:12.46,Normal Dialog Text,Garnet,0,0,0,,{\fn微软雅黑\fs64\c&H811CC0&}抓住橄榄石并不能让一切回归正常\N{\fnArial\fs48}Catching Peridot won't make things go back to normal.
Dialogue: 100,0:07:12.94,0:07:14.38,Normal Dialog Text,Garnet,0,0,0,,{\fn微软雅黑\fs64\c&H811CC0&}这和橄榄石无关\N{\fnArial\fs48}This isn't about Peridot.
Dialogue: 100,0:07:14.96,0:07:17.12,Normal Dialog Text,General,0,0,0,,{\fn微软雅黑\fs64}嘿！她们开始相互说话了\N{\fnArial\fs48}Hey, they're actually talking.
Dialogue: 100,0:07:17.26,0:07:19.24,Normal Dialog Text,General,0,0,0,,{\fn微软雅黑\fs64}现在她们总算能解决问题了\N{\fnArial\fs48}Now they can finally work things out.
Dialogue: 100,0:07:24.74,0:07:26.56,Normal Dialog Text,General,0,0,0,,{\fn微软雅黑\fs64}除非她们被压碎！\N{\fnArial\fs48}Not if they get crushed!
Dialogue: 100,0:07:29.42,0:07:31.18,Normal Dialog Text,General,0,0,0,,{\fn微软雅黑\fs64}请告诉我！\N{\fnArial\fs48}Please tell me!
Dialogue: 100,0:07:31.92,0:07:33.96,Normal Dialog Text,General,0,0,0,,{\fn微软雅黑\fs64}我怎样才能让你原谅我？\N{\fnArial\fs48}How can I make you forgive me?!
Dialogue: 100,0:07:34.14,0:07:35.94,Normal Dialog Text,General,0,0,0,,{\fn微软雅黑\fs64}无论如何都不能！你欺骗了我\N{\fnArial\fs48}You can't. You lied to me.
Dialogue: 100,0:07:36.18,0:07:39.06,Normal Dialog Text,General,0,0,0,,{\fn微软雅黑\fs64}你必须认识到你的所作所为会有后果的\N{\fnArial\fs48}You need to learn that there are consequences to your actions.
Dialogue: 100,0:07:39.38,0:07:43.78,Normal Dialog Text,General,0,0,0,,{\fn微软雅黑\fs64}我对不起，我...我不能控制住自己\N{\fnArial\fs48} I'm sorry. I...I couldn't help myself.
Dialogue: 100,0:07:43.78,0:07:45.78,Normal Dialog Text,General,0,0,0,,{\fn微软雅黑\fs64}我不想听你的借口！\N{\fnArial\fs48}I don't want to hear your excuses.
Dialogue: 100,0:07:46.16,0:07:47.32,Normal Dialog Text,General,0,0,0,,{\fn微软雅黑\fs64}但这是真的\N{\fnArial\fs48}But it's true.
Dialogue: 100,0:07:47.32,0:07:50.92,Normal Dialog Text,General,0,0,0,,{\fn微软雅黑\fs64}不论我如何尝试像你一样强大\N{\fnArial\fs48}No matter how hard I try to be strong like you,
Dialogue: 100,0:07:51.14,0:07:52.32,Normal Dialog Text,General,0,0,0,,{\fn微软雅黑\fs64}我仍只是个珍珠\N{\fnArial\fs48}I'm just a Pearl.
Dialogue: 100,0:07:52.80,0:07:54.20,Normal Dialog Text,General,0,0,0,,{\fn微软雅黑\fs64}我独自一人时一无是处\N{\fnArial\fs48}I'm useless on my own.
Dialogue: 100,0:07:54.56,0:07:57.20,Normal Dialog Text,General,0,0,0,,{\fn微软雅黑\fs64}我需要有人告诉我做什么\N{\fnArial\fs48}I need someone to tell me what to do.
Dialogue: 100,0:08:04.12,0:08:07.56,Normal Dialog Text,General,0,0,0,,{\fn微软雅黑\fs64}当我们融合时，我能体会到作为你的感觉\N{\fnArial\fs48}When we fuse, I can feel what it's like to be you.
Dialogue: 100,0:08:08.02,0:08:10.30,Normal Dialog Text,General,0,0,0,,{\fn微软雅黑\fs64}自信，有安全感，充实\N{\fnArial\fs48}Confident and secure and complete.
Dialogue: 100,0:08:11.02,0:08:11.90,Normal Dialog Text,General,0,0,0,,{\fn微软雅黑\fs64}你是如此完美\N{\fnArial\fs48}You're perfect.
Dialogue: 100,0:08:12.14,0:08:13.82,Normal Dialog Text,General,0,0,0,,{\fn微软雅黑\fs64}你是一个完美的关系\N{\fnArial\fs48}You're the perfect relationship.
Dialogue: 100,0:08:14.10,0:08:15.04,Normal Dialog Text,General,0,0,0,,{\fn微软雅黑\fs64}你们总是在一起\N{\fnArial\fs48}You're always together.
Dialogue: 100,0:08:15.04,0:08:17.30,Normal Dialog Text,General,0,0,0,,{\fn微软雅黑\fs64}我只是-我想成为其中的一部分\N{\fnArial\fs48}I just -- I wanted to be a part of that.
Dialogue: 100,0:08:17.64,0:08:18.38,Normal Dialog Text,General,0,0,0,,{\fn微软雅黑\fs64}你错了\N{\fnArial\fs48}You're wrong.
Dialogue: 100,0:08:19.10,0:08:20.50,Normal Dialog Text,General,0,0,0,,{\fn微软雅黑\fs64}我没你想的那么强大\N{\fnArial\fs48}I'm not as strong as you think.
Dialogue: 100,0:08:21.14,0:08:22.74,Normal Dialog Text,General,0,0,0,,{\fn微软雅黑\fs64}我-我因为这件事破裂了\N{\fnArial\fs48}I-I fell apart over this.
Dialogue: 100,0:08:23.16,0:08:26.18,Normal Dialog Text,General,0,0,0,,{\fn微软雅黑\fs64}红宝石和蓝宝石因为你蒙骗我吵得不可开交\N{\fnArial\fs48}Ruby and Sapphire were in turmoil over how you deceived me.
Dialogue: 100,0:08:26.60,0:08:27.80,Normal Dialog Text,Garnet,0,0,0,,{\fn微软雅黑\fs64\c&H811CC0&}我瓦解了\N{\fnArial\fs48}I came undone.
Dialogue: 100,0:08:27.98,0:08:29.66,Normal Dialog Text,General,0,0,0,,{\fn微软雅黑\fs64}喔，那真的发生了？\N{\fnArial\fs48}Whoa. That really happened?
Dialogue: 100,0:08:29.84,0:08:30.14,Normal Dialog Text,General,0,0,0,,{\fn微软雅黑\fs64}嗯\N{\fnArial\fs48}Hmm.
Dialogue: 100,0:08:30.70,0:08:32.50,Normal Dialog Text,General,0,0,0,,{\fn微软雅黑\fs64}掌控一切并不容易\N{\fnArial\fs48}It's not easy being in control.
Dialogue: 100,0:08:32.84,0:08:34.02,Normal Dialog Text,General,0,0,0,,{\fn微软雅黑\fs64}我也有弱点\N{\fnArial\fs48}I have weaknesses, too,
Dialogue: 100,0:08:34.26,0:08:36.16,Normal Dialog Text,General,0,0,0,,{\fn微软雅黑\fs64}但我选择不让弱点占上风\N{\fnArial\fs48}but I choose not to let them consume me.
Dialogue: 100,0:08:36.36,0:08:37.58,Normal Dialog Text,General,0,0,0,,{\fn微软雅黑\fs64}我努力保持强大\N{\fnArial\fs48}I struggle to stay strong
Dialogue: 100,0:08:37.58,0:08:39.88,Normal Dialog Text,General,0,0,0,,{\fn微软雅黑\fs64}因为我知道我对其他人的巨大影响力\N{\fnArial\fs48}because I know the impact I have on everyone.
Dialogue: 100,0:08:40.80,0:08:43.92,Normal Dialog Text,Garnet,0,0,0,,{\fn微软雅黑\fs64\c&H811CC0&}一定要明白，珍珠，你也有影响力\N{\fnArial\fs48}Please understand, Pearl, you have an impact, too.
Dialogue: 100,0:08:44.32,0:08:46.46,Normal Dialog Text,General,0,0,0,,{\fn微软雅黑\fs64}很多次我都将你视为力量的象征\N{\fnArial\fs48}There are times when I look up to you for strength.
Dialogue: 100,0:08:46.72,0:08:48.58,Normal Dialog Text,General,0,0,0,,{\fn微软雅黑\fs64}你是为你自己而存在的宝石人\N{\fnArial\fs48}You are your own gem.
Dialogue: 100,0:08:49.10,0:08:50.66,Normal Dialog Text,General,0,0,0,,{\fn微软雅黑\fs64}你控制着自己的命运\N{\fnArial\fs48}You control your destiny.
Dialogue: 100,0:08:50.94,0:08:53.58,Normal Dialog Text,General,0,0,0,,{\fn微软雅黑\fs64}而不是我，或者玫瑰，或者史蒂文\N{\fnArial\fs48}Not me, not Rose, not Steven.
Dialogue: 100,0:08:53.92,0:08:57.18,Normal Dialog Text,General,0,0,0,,{\fn微软雅黑\fs64}但你必须选择变得强大，然后我们才能前行，\N{\fnArial\fs48}But you must choose to be strong so we can move forward,
Dialogue: 100,0:08:57.52,0:08:58.80,Normal Dialog Text,General,0,0,0,,{\fn微软雅黑\fs64}然后我才能再次信任你\N{\fnArial\fs48}so I can trust you again.
Dialogue: 100,0:08:59.92,0:09:03.08,Normal Dialog Text,General,0,0,0,,{\fn微软雅黑\fs64}我理解了，我不能再自暴自弃了\N{\fnArial\fs48}I understand. I can't give up anymore.
Dialogue: 100,0:09:03.44,0:09:03.82,Normal Dialog Text,General,0,0,0,,{\fn微软雅黑\fs64}很好\N{\fnArial\fs48}Good.
Dialogue: 100,0:09:09.02,0:09:11.44,Normal Dialog Text,General,0,0,0,,{\fn微软雅黑\fs64}珍珠，现在只有一个方法能解决问题\N{\fnArial\fs48}Pearl, there's only one way out of this.
Dialogue: 100,0:09:12.20,0:09:13.64,Normal Dialog Text,General,0,0,0,,{\fn微软雅黑\fs64}只要你愿意的话\N{\fnArial\fs48}Only if you're okay with it.
Dialogue: 100,0:09:14.28,0:09:14.76,Normal Dialog Text,General,0,0,0,,{\fn微软雅黑\fs64}嗯\N{\fnArial\fs48}Mm.
Dialogue: 100,0:09:15.44,0:09:16.44,Normal Dialog Text,General,0,0,0,,{\fn微软雅黑\fs64}啊！\N{\fnArial\fs48}Aah!
Dialogue: 100,0:09:16.44,0:09:19.38,Normal Dialog Text,General,0,0,0,,{\fn微软雅黑\fs64}怎么办？怎么办？怎么办？怎么办？\N{\fnArial\fs48}What do we do?! What do we do?! What do we do?! What do we do?!
Dialogue: 600,0:09:21.70,0:09:23.95,Hint,,0,0,0,,{\pos(960,50)}红玛瑙手中的钻头与《天元突破-红莲螺岩》中的钻头武器类似
Dialogue: 100,0:09:31.58,0:09:32.68,Normal Dialog Text,General,0,0,0,,{\fn微软雅黑\fs64}这个垃圾按钮\N{\fnArial\fs48}Stupid button here.
Dialogue: 100,0:09:32.68,0:09:34.82,Normal Dialog Text,General,0,0,0,,{\fn微软雅黑\fs64}我不知道还有什么-啊～！\N{\fnArial\fs48}I don't know what anything is -- aah!
Dialogue: 100,0:09:35.02,0:09:36.62,Normal Dialog Text,General,0,0,0,,{\fn微软雅黑\fs64}炸了这堆宝石古董！\N{\fnArial\fs48}Blast this old gem tech!
Dialogue: 100,0:09:37.14,0:09:40.04,Normal Dialog Text,General,0,0,0,,{\fn微软雅黑\fs64}她们去哪了？为什么没东西能工作？！\N{\fnArial\fs48}Where did they go? Why isn't anything working?!
Dialogue: 100,0:09:40.30,0:09:41.34,Normal Dialog Text,General,0,0,0,,{\fn微软雅黑\fs64}啊～！\N{\fnArial\fs48}Aah!
Dialogue: 100,0:09:41.62,0:09:42.86,Normal Dialog Text,General,0,0,0,,{\fn微软雅黑\fs64}投降吧，橄榄石\N{\fnArial\fs48}Surrender, Peridot.
Dialogue: 100,0:09:43.12,0:09:44.26,Normal Dialog Text,General,0,0,0,,{\fn微软雅黑\fs64}你无处可逃了\N{\fnArial\fs48}You have nowhere to run.
Dialogue: 100,0:09:44.66,0:09:47.58,Normal Dialog Text,General,0,0,0,,{\fn微软雅黑\fs64}水晶战士-要抓住你了！\N{\fnArial\fs48}The Crystal Gems are gonna get you.
Dialogue: 100,0:09:47.80,0:09:49.94,Normal Dialog Text,General,0,0,0,,{\fn微软雅黑\fs64}你们真以为就结束了？\N{\fnArial\fs48}You really think this is the end?
Dialogue: 100,0:09:51.56,0:09:54.22,Normal Dialog Text,General,0,0,0,,{\fn微软雅黑\fs64}这-这才只是开端...\N{\fnArial\fs48}This -- this is only the beginning...
Dialogue: 100,0:09:55.36,0:09:57.02,Normal Dialog Text,General,0,0,0,,{\fn微软雅黑\fs64}我跑路的开端\N{\fnArial\fs48}Of my escape.
Dialogue: 100,0:10:02.08,0:10:03.44,Normal Dialog Text,General,0,0,0,,{\fn微软雅黑\fs64}其实，我很想留下来\N{\fnArial\fs48}Well, I'd love to stick around
Dialogue: 100,0:10:03.44,0:10:06.52,Normal Dialog Text,General,0,0,0,,{\fn微软雅黑\fs64}观看你们另一次可悲的抓捕我的无用功\N{\fnArial\fs48}and watch another one of your pathetic attempts to capture me,
Dialogue: 100,0:10:06.86,0:10:08.48,Normal Dialog Text,General,0,0,0,,{\fn微软雅黑\fs64}但我想我实在太聪明了\N{\fnArial\fs48}but I guess I'm just too smart
Dialogue: 100,0:10:08.48,0:10:10.94,Normal Dialog Text,General,0,0,0,,{\fn微软雅黑\fs64}相比于你们这群愚蠢臃肿的草包！\N{\fnArial\fs48}for the likes of you lumpy, clumpy clods.
Dialogue: 100,0:10:14.16,0:10:15.06,Normal Dialog Text,General,0,0,0,,{\fn微软雅黑\fs64}搞毛？\N{\fnArial\fs48}What the?
Dialogue: 100,0:10:15.12,0:10:16.90,Normal Dialog Text,General,0,0,0,,{\fn微软雅黑\fs64}我抓到只橄榄石哦\N{\fnArial\fs48}I caught a Peridot.
