Dialogue: 100,0:10:17.06,0:10:20.82,Normal Dialog Text,General,0,0,0,,{\fn微软雅黑\fs64}嘿！将你的触碰肢从我身上拿开，你个史蒂文\N{\fnArial\fs48}Hey, get your touch stumps off me, you Steven.
Dialogue: 100,0:10:21.98,0:10:22.82,Normal Dialog Text,General,0,0,0,,{\fn微软雅黑\fs64}嘿！\N{\fnArial\fs48}Hey!
Dialogue: 100,0:10:23.42,0:10:24.68,Normal Dialog Text,General,0,0,0,,{\fn微软雅黑\fs64}坚持住，史蒂文！\N{\fnArial\fs48}Yeah, Steven!
Dialogue: 100,0:10:24.68,0:10:25.88,Normal Dialog Text,General,0,0,0,,{\fn微软雅黑\fs64}别放走她\N{\fnArial\fs48}Don't let her go.
Dialogue: 100,0:10:30.52,0:10:31.86,Normal Dialog Text,General,0,0,0,,{\fn微软雅黑\fs64}放开我！\N{\fnArial\fs48}Let go of me!
Dialogue: 100,0:10:32.16,0:10:37.00,Normal Dialog Text,General,0,0,0,,{\fn微软雅黑\fs64}你-你个顽固，矮挫的鬼东西\N{\fnArial\fs48}You -- you persistent, little whatever exactly you are!
Dialogue: 100,0:10:37.00,0:10:40.16,Normal Dialog Text,General,0,0,0,,{\fn微软雅黑\fs64}橄榄石，你的航班，被取消了！\N{\fnArial\fs48}Peridot, your flight's been canceled.
Dialogue: 100,0:10:40.16,0:10:41.52,Normal Dialog Text,General,0,0,0,,{\fn微软雅黑\fs64}不~！\N{\fnArial\fs48}No!
