Dialogue: 100,0:10:45.88,0:10:47.80,Normal Dialog Text,General,0,0,0,,{\fn微软雅黑\fs64}你们会付出代价的，水晶战士\N{\fnArial\fs48}You'll pay for this, crystal gems.
Dialogue: 100,0:10:47.80,0:10:49.14,Normal Dialog Text,General,0,0,0,,{\fn微软雅黑\fs64}我迟早会报复的\N{\fnArial\fs48}I'll get you back.
Dialogue: 100,0:10:49.14,0:10:51.88,Normal Dialog Text,General,0,0,0,,{\fn微软雅黑\fs64}你们给我等着～！\N{\fnArial\fs48}Just you wa-a-a-it!
Dialogue: 100,0:10:57.98,0:10:58.44,Normal Dialog Text,General,0,0,0,,{\fn微软雅黑\fs64}珍珠？\N{\fnArial\fs48}Pearl?
Dialogue: 100,0:10:59.06,0:11:00.04,Normal Dialog Text,General,0,0,0,,{\fn微软雅黑\fs64}这不算什么，史蒂文\N{\fnArial\fs48}It's okay, Steven.
Dialogue: 100,0:11:00.50,0:11:02.74,Normal Dialog Text,General,0,0,0,,{\fn微软雅黑\fs64}下次，我们就能抓到她生下的部分了\N{\fnArial\fs48}Next time, we'll get the rest of her.
Dialogue: 100,0:11:03.10,0:11:03.86,Normal Dialog Text,General,0,0,0,,{\fn微软雅黑\fs64}对吧，石榴？\N{\fnArial\fs48}Right, Garnet?
Dialogue: 100,0:11:04.34,0:11:05.32,Normal Dialog Text,General,0,0,0,,{\fn微软雅黑\fs64}这是坚实的一步\N{\fnArial\fs48}It's a good step forward.
